manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Rockland 4 Piece Softside Upright Luggage Set This deluxe 4-piece expandable luggage set is manufactured with a patented heavy duty EVA-molded hi-count fabric. Made with the very best heavy duty polyester and PVC backing, this luggage set is designed for the traveler on the go and comes with three expandable uprights and a flight tote bag. A variety of colors and patterns are available for ever taste! Carry-on upright: 20"x 12.5"x 7.5" (with wheels) 24-inch Upright: 24"x16"x10" 28-inch Upright: 28"x18"x12" Tote: 14"x11"x5"

Features and Design Telescoping Handle The telescoping handle stows away conveniently and allows for easy maneuvering when extended. Expandable The upright expands an extra 2 inches in depth to maximize your packing capacity. Sturdy Inline Wheels Two sturdy inline wheels allow for easy transport of your belongings.

About Rockland Luggage Since its inception in 1998, Rockland by Fox Luggage has been proudly producing quality luggage and bags for the style savvy traveler. Recognized for its graphic and colorful designs, Rockland prides itself on creating products influenced by current trends in design and fashion. Our products turn heads in a crowd and stand out in the baggage carousel, making it easy for quick exits out the airport. Affordable and travel resistant, Rockland bags are an ideal companion for everything from quick trips to the gym to overnight getaways to extended vacations. Our selection includes: luggage sets (4 piece, 3 piece or 2 piece), hard cases, soft cases, carry ons, rolling backpacks, travel duffels, rolling duffels, cosmetic bags, and kids' backpacks. Over the years, a few Rockland products have been featured in film and television. Their colorful designs make them ideal for an eye catching visual element on screen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Good for price. 5thousand miles still in good shape. Zipper on pocket got stuck on carry on. No big deal. Good buy. No complaints for price. Last suitcase set got me 200 miles and wheels broken, zippers broken, couldn't use again. That set cost100 dollars more than this one..plastic hard shell. Another set with the100 dollar carry-on fell off the luggage cart and cracked.. This is a good buy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice if you don’t travel a lot
reviews.reviewText: Good quality great price. Not very heavy duty so if you travel a lot this probably isn’t for you. The color makes it great to find

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nicer than expected but too big and thin.
reviews.reviewText: I was willing to try these on our trip with Southwest Airlines, but 2 of the 4 pcs would need checked. It looked like the 2 smaller ones & tote were small enough to carry on, but with the handle and wheels the 24" was actually 25.5" tall. The back is thin as to be expected at this price. It did have an interior liner to keep stuff falling out if it the outer back ripped during transit. The compartments we're large and the front was really nice, but with .3 out of every 100,000 (30,000) checked bags reporting theft, we need to carry on as much as possible. This luggage just wouldn't allow that. I would also worry it'd be easy to cut into. The tote was roomier than expected. All toiletries would most likely fit inside.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Grat luggage set at a great price!
reviews.reviewText: When packing for a trip in a few days I found out that my suitcase was broken so I quickly came on Amazon and found these beauties! I ordered the 4-piece set in purple and the color is amazing, I love it!!! It is a very nice dark purple so it will hide dirt and wear and tear nicely!Seems sturdy; hasn't fallen over when standing upright. Wheel maneuver nicely and all zippers, handles, etc. are in good working order and easy to manipulate. I highly recommend this luggage set (my other half has the same in a different color and has had it several years w/out any problems). With a price like this you really can't go wrong purchasing this item!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I don't like the zipper ,it's not smooth operating and the locks that come with it a cheaply made ,I purchased the set because the color stands out when looking for it on airport carousel the price was pretty good

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice find-perfect for light travel for a family
reviews.reviewText: Nice luggage set. We are not huge travelers at this point in our lives but it's been a while since we purchased a set and just needed something to travel with a few times a year. Under 100.00 for this 4 piece is perfect. We looked at soo many other options, fancy ones, hard shells etc decided to go with just a standard set.. it really provides all the room we need and serves it's purpose. We can comfortably pack for our family of four -2 adults, a teen boy and younger girl for about a week to 10 days with this size set. Handles seem sturdy, the zippers are made well, has your average buckles, nets and liners on the inside. Glad we went with this set and would absolutely buy again.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars You get what you get.
reviews.reviewText: These suitcases are affordable for how many you get. Not the most durable, but they got the job done for us. My biggest complaint is that they do not stand on their own if you have things inside. Maybe my packing skills need to improve, but the thing just falls over and cannot balance when you’ve got stuff in it. Not the biggest deal, but frustrating when you need to use both hands and it tips right over.
